{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Vision Zero is an international road saftey effort with the goal of ending fatalities and serious injuries related to road traffic. <a href=\"https://www.boston.gov/transportation/vision-zero\">Vision Zero Boston</a> is the City’s local program. As part of that effort, the City tracks traffic crashes and fatalities on the <a href=\"https://apps.boston.gov/vision-zero/\">Vision Zero Crash Map</a>.</p>\n<p>In Summer 2018, we re-built the crash map to bring it inline with Boston’s branding, modernize the technology stack, and automate the updating process. The map now leverages <a href=\"https://postgis.net/\">PostGIS</a>, <a href=\"https://docs.mapbox.com/mapbox-gl-js/api/\">Mapbox GL JS</a>, and <a href=\"https://nextjs.org/\">React/NextJS</a>.</p>\n<p>The crash and fatality data can be found on <a href=\"https://data.boston.gov/dataset?organization=vision-zero-boston-program&#x26;q=vision+zero\">Analyze Boston</a>, the City’s open data portal.</p>\n<p>The <a href=\"https://github.com/CityOfBoston/vision-zero\">code for the map</a> can be found on github.</p>\n<div class=\"imageBlock\">\n    <div>\n        <a href=\"https://github.com/CityOfBoston/vision-zero\">\n            <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\" style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 700px;\">\n    <span class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\" style=\"padding-bottom: 57.14285714285714%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url(&apos;data:image/jpeg;base64,&apos;); background-size: cover; display: block;\"></span>\n    <img class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\" style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\" alt=\"Figure 1\" title src=\"/static/ad79a9222ef4243d7ee256413a589f97/5e590/vision-zero.jpg\" srcset=\"/static/ad79a9222ef4243d7ee256413a589f97/090a8/vision-zero.jpg 225w,\n/static/ad79a9222ef4243d7ee256413a589f97/3c058/vision-zero.jpg 450w,\n/static/ad79a9222ef4243d7ee256413a589f97/5e590/vision-zero.jpg 700w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\">\n  </span>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</div>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vision Zero Crash Map"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/projects/vision-zero/"}}